@startuml
actor "HR Manager" as HR
participant "System" as SYS
participant "Payroll Module" as PAY
participant "Database" as DB

HR -> SYS: Request Payroll Calculation
SYS -> PAY: Start Calculation
PAY -> DB: Fetch Employee Data
DB --> PAY: Employee Records
PAY -> PAY: Calculate Salaries (base - deductions + benefits)
PAY -> DB: Save Payroll Results
DB --> PAY: Confirmation
PAY --> SYS: Payroll Report Generated
SYS --> HR: Display Payroll Report
@enduml
